<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="wrong-adj">wrong <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /rɒŋ/    美 /rɔːŋ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>错误的；不正确的：</strong></h4>
<p>反 right </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Sorry, you have the <strong>wrong number</strong>. 
对不起，你打错电话了。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>You’re <strong>wrong about</strong> Tom; he hasn’t married at all.
你弄错了，汤姆根本没有结婚。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>You’re wrong to leave your child alone at home.
你不应该让孩子单独待在家里。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>不道德的：</strong></h4>
<p>反 right </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Telling lies is wrong. 
撒谎是不对的。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>It was wrong</strong> of you <strong>to</strong> steal money. 
你偷钱是不对的。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>出故障的；有毛病的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>There was something wrong with</strong> my computer yesterday.
昨天我的电脑坏了。</p></div>

<h4 id="4">4.★ <strong>不合适的：</strong></h4>
<p>反 right </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>This is the wrong time to make a visit. 
这不是拜访的时候。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="whats-wrong-with">What’s wrong with …?</h3>
<p>1.<strong>…怎么了？</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I don’t know what’s wrong with the engine. 
我不知道引擎出了什么问题。</p></div></div>